QuestData.Title: Thieving Thistleleaf
QuestData.Description: Why the Thistleleaf are collecting the Lunarwing eggs is anyone's guess, but you can be sure it's not to give them a loving home.$b$bSaylanna Riverbreeze will know what to do with these.
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect $1oa Stolen Lunarwing Eggs in the Lunarwing Shallows.
QuestData.CompletionText: Gather as many eggs as you can and bring them back to me. I will keep them safe.
QuestData.RewardText: Until I can discover what is vexing the Thistleleaf, I'll have to look after the Lunarwing eggs. At least I know they will be safe.
